HEADWORD: Pentachenium
<hw>Pen`ta*che"ni*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Penta-</er>, and <er>Achenium</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
